;ARGS:0　シチュ指定　ARGS:1,2　さらに細かく振り分けたい場合に使用
@KOJO_GENERAL_INDEX_専用口上ベース(ARGS:0,ARGS:1,ARGS:2,ARGS:3)

SELECTCASE ARGS:0
CASE "Example"
	{
	CALL MESSAGE_BOX,@"--------\nThis [Exclusive Dialogue Base] is for those who want to display only the parts written in the dedicated script to prevent speech distortion.\n
	No other scripts apart from the example shown here are set up.\n
	If you have set a dedicated script but this example is being displayed,\n
	It is likely that the [Example] is not set in the dedicated script file."
	}

ENDSELECT

